00:24:07.028 --> 00:24:09.990
So pinaglalaruan lang nila kami
the whole time, tapos?

00:24:12.909 --> 00:24:15.579
Kaya walang anumang mataas na kapangyarihan
na gumagawa ng lahat ng ito?

00:24:16.455 --> 00:24:17.497
Tao lang sila?

00:24:21.501 --> 00:24:22.752
Ngunit posible na…

00:24:24.379 --> 00:24:26.965
