Mas malaya na ako kaysa dati.

00:30:44.509 --> 00:30:46.594
Ito na ang katapusan ng ating paraiso.

00:30:54.769 --> 00:30:56.646
Kaya marami sa atin ang namatay.

00:31:17.333 --> 00:31:18.459
Hindi ko akalain na…

00:31:19.502 --> 00:31:20.795
mapapatawad sila kailanman.

00:31:23.047 --> 00:31:25.425
- Bitawan mo ako!
- Hindi mo kaya.

00:31:28.678 --> 00:31:29.804
Pero sila…

00:31:30.889 --> 00:31:32.473
Pinatay nila silang lahat!

00:31:33.224 --> 00:31:34.517
Hindi ko kayang bitawan yun!

